{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLSlotElement.assignedNodes()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/assignedNodes","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement\"><code>HTMLSlotElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/name\"><code>name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/assign\"><code>assign()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/assignedElements\"><code>assignedElements()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>assignedNodes()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ereignisse</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/slotchange_event\"><code>slotchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die Eigenschaft <strong><code>assignedNodes()</code></strong> der Schnittstelle <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement\"><code>HTMLSlotElement</code></a> gibt die Reihenfolge der diesem Slot zugewiesenen Elemente oder alternativ den Fallback-Inhalt des Slots zurück.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var assignedNodes[] = HTMLSlotElement.assignedNodes([options])</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"options\">options <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>Ein Objekt, das Optionen für die zurückzugebenden Knoten festlegt. Die verfügbaren Optionen sind:\n <ul>\n  <li><code>flatten</code>: Ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a>, das angibt, ob die dem Slot zugewiesenen Elemente zurückgegeben werden sollen (wenn dieser Wert <code>false</code>&nbsp;ist) oder der Fallback-Inhalt des Slots (wenn dieser Wert <code>true</code>&nbsp;ist). Die Vorgabe ist <code>false</code>.</li>\n </ul>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewerte","title":"Rückgabewerte","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ein Array von Knoten.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das folgende Schnippsel ist unserem <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/web-components-examples/tree/master/slotchange\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Slotchange-Beispiel</a> entnommen (<a href=\"https://mdn.github.io/web-components-examples/slotchange/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">siehe auch live</a>).</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> slots <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shadowRoot<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelectorAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'slot'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nslots<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'slotchange'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> nodes <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> slots<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">assignedNodes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Element in Slot \"'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> slots<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\" changed to \"'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> nodes<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>outerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\".'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Hier nehmen wir Verweise auf alle Slots und fügen dann einen Slotchange Event Listener zum zweiten Slot in der Vorlage hinzu - derjenige, dessen Inhalt im Beispiel geändert wird.</p>\n\n<p>Jedes Mal, wenn sich das in den Slot eingefügte Element ändert, protokollieren wir einen Bericht an die Konsole, aus dem hervorgeht, welcher Slot sich geändert hat und was der neue Knoten im Slot ist.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#dom-slot-assignednodes\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'assignedNodes' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLSlotElement.assignedNodes","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/assignedNodes/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"}],"summary":"Die Eigenschaft assignedNodes() der Schnittstelle HTMLSlotElement gibt die Reihenfolge der diesem Slot zugewiesenen Elemente oder alternativ den Fallback-Inhalt des Slots zurück.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLSlotElement.assignedNodes()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLSlotElement.assignedNodes()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/htmlslotelement/assignednodes","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/htmlslotelement/assignednodes/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement","title":"HTMLSlotElement"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/assignedNodes","title":"HTMLSlotElement.assignedNodes()"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLSlotElement.assignedNodes() - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}